{"name":"Baba Yaga the Child Witch - descriptor-darkego.cazador","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01343uy401h7ue11","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Baba yaga The Child Witch","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","ownerKey":"cazador.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Baba Yaga la Niña Bruja - descriptor-darkego.cazador","system":{"description":"<p>Como cualquier hechicera respetable, llevo mi fiel bolsa llena de hierbas, venenos y todo tipo de herramientas mágicas. Mi aspecto infantil suele ser útil, pero a veces hace que los demás me subestimen. Odio eso.</p>","positive":"<p>Como cualquier hechicera respetable, llevo mi fiel bolsa llena de hierbas, venenos y todo tipo de herramientas mágicas. Mi aspecto infantil suele ser útil, pero a veces hace que los demás me subestimen. Odio eso.</p>"},"description":"<p>Como cualquier hechicera respetable, llevo mi fiel bolsa llena de hierbas, venenos y todo tipo de herramientas mágicas. Mi aspecto infantil <br>suele ser útil, pero a veces hace que los demás me subestimen. Odio eso.</p>"}},"ownerName":"Baba Yaga the Child Witch","ownerNameEs":"Baba Yaga la Niña Bruja","key":"descriptor-darkego.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"Like any respectable sorceress, I carry my trusty bag full of herbs, poisons, and all kinds of magic tools. My childlike appearance is often useful, but sometimes it leads others to underestimate me. I hate that.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 10.","positive":"Like any respectable sorceress, I carry my trusty bag full of herbs, poisons, and all kinds of magic tools. My childlike appearance is often useful, but sometimes it leads others to underestimate me. I hate that.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"baba-yaga-the-child-witch","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.cazador"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"dd876030afa97d7f"}
{"name":"Baba Yaga the Child Witch - descriptor-principal.cazador","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","system":{"description":"I am a child witch, and my power is equal only to my ambition. I did not have a childhood, for I was born already aware of my abilities. To most, I seem cynical and cruel. That is because they do not understand that they are pawns, insignificant pieces in the bloody games that witches and warlocks play. The Order does not look down on my age, which is why it has given me the leadership I deserve.","notes":"","source":{"title":"Core Book","pages":""},"key":"descriptor-principal.cazador","category":"hunter","owner":"baba-yaga-the-child-witch"},"flags":{"broken-tales":{"contentKey":"descriptor-principal.cazador.baba.yaga.the.child.witch","ownerKey":"hunter.baba.yaga.the.child.witch","descriptorRole":"principal-descriptor","contentSort":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Baba Yaga la Niña Bruja - descriptor-principal.cazador","system":{"description":"<p>Soy una niña bruja, y mi poder solo es equiparable a mi ambición. No tuve infancia, pues nací ya consciente de mis capacidades. A la mayoría les parezco cínica y cruel. Eso es porque no comprenden que son peones, piezas insignificantes en los sangrientos juegos que juegan brujas y brujos. La Orden no me desprecia por mi edad, por eso me ha dado el liderazgo que merezco. Como cualquier hechicera respetable, llevo mi fiel bolsa llena de hierbas, venenos y todo tipo de herramientas mágicas. Mi aspecto infantil suele ser útil, pero a veces hace que los demás me subestimen. Odio eso.</p>"}}},"embeddedSource":"hunter-descriptors-canon","sequence":0,"ownerName":"Baba Yaga the Child Witch","ownerNameEs":"Baba Yaga la Niña Bruja","key":"descriptor-principal.cazador"}},"folder":"01343uy401h7ue11","sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"effects":[],"_id":"c51d1b097c8e16cd"}
{"name":"Baba Yaga the Child Witch - descriptor1-don1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01343uy401h7ue11","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Baba yaga The Child Witch","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","ownerKey":"cazador.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Baba Yaga la Niña Bruja - descriptor1-don1","system":{"description":"<p>Soy una hechicera y mis poderes mágicos me permiten hacer lo que quiera. Necesito el tiempo adecuado para lanzar mis hechizos.</p>","positive":"<p>Soy una hechicera y mis poderes mágicos me permiten hacer lo que quiera. Necesito el tiempo adecuado para lanzar mis hechizos.</p>"},"description":"<p>Soy una hechicera y mis poderes mágicos me permiten hacer <br>lo que quiera. Necesito el tiempo adecuado para lanzar mis <br>hechizos.</p>"}},"ownerName":"Baba Yaga the Child Witch","ownerNameEs":"Baba Yaga la Niña Bruja","key":"descriptor1-don1.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"I am a sorceress and my magical powers allow me to do whatever I want. I need the right amount of time to cast my spells.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 10.","positive":"I am a sorceress and my magical powers allow me to do whatever I want. I need the right amount of time to cast my spells.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"baba-yaga-the-child-witch","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.cazador"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"97cf6e654aea8300"}
{"name":"Baba Yaga the Child Witch - descriptor2-don2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01343uy401h7ue11","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Baba yaga The Child Witch","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","ownerKey":"cazador.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Baba Yaga la Niña Bruja - descriptor2-don2","system":{"description":"<p>Soy muy hábil analizando a la gente, por eso la Orden me ha elegido como líder de los Cazadores. Me encanta manipular a la gente y a menudo lo hago solo para divertirme.</p>","positive":"<p>Soy muy hábil analizando a la gente, por eso la Orden me ha elegido como líder de los Cazadores. Me encanta manipular a la gente y a menudo lo hago solo para divertirme.</p>"},"description":"<p>Soy muy hábil analizando a la gente, por eso la Orden me ha <br>elegido como líder de los Cazadores. Me encanta manipular a <br>la gente y a menudo lo hago solo para divertirme.</p>"}},"ownerName":"Baba Yaga the Child Witch","ownerNameEs":"Baba Yaga la Niña Bruja","key":"descriptor2-don2.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"I am very skilled at reading people, that is why the Order has chosen me as leader of the Hunters. I love manipulating people and I often do it merely to amuse myself.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 10.","positive":"I am very skilled at reading people, that is why the Order has chosen me as leader of the Hunters. I love manipulating people and I often do it merely to amuse myself.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"baba-yaga-the-child-witch","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.cazador"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"b5ad7c0bafc17292"}
{"name":"Babai the Judge - descriptor-darkego.cazador","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01rery4l01en0umi","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Babai the Judge","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.babai-the-judge","ownerKey":"cazador.babai-the-judge","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Babai el Juez - descriptor-darkego.cazador","system":{"description":"<p>Mi presencia intimida a la gente, rozando el miedo que habita en lo más profundo de su corazón. La presencia de los niños y su inocente forma de ver el mundo me inquieta.</p>","positive":"<p>Mi presencia intimida a la gente, rozando el miedo que habita en lo más profundo de su corazón. La presencia de los niños y su inocente forma de ver el mundo me inquieta.</p>"},"description":"<p>Mi presencia intimida a la gente, rozando el miedo que habita en lo <br>más profundo de su corazón. La presencia de los niños y su inocente <br>forma de ver el mundo me inquieta.</p>"}},"ownerName":"Babai the Judge","ownerNameEs":"Babai el Juez","key":"descriptor-darkego.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"My presence intimidates people, touching the fear that dwells deep in their hearts. The presence of children and their innocent way of looking at the world makes me uneasy.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 14.","positive":"My presence intimidates people, touching the fear that dwells deep in their hearts. The presence of children and their innocent way of looking at the world makes me uneasy.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"babai-the-judge","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.cazador"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"8ba89213a42deb8c"}
{"name":"Babai the Judge - descriptor-principal.cazador","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","system":{"description":"After years of honorable service as State Inquisitor of the Republic of Venice, my body and spirit have undergone a rare mutation and fear is now unknown to me. People have always called me Bogeyman, fearing the justice that I represented. Perhaps my own absence of fear made me even more terrifying in the eyes of mortals. The Order has given me a new assignment because even in the fight against darkness, someone needs to be ready to judge what is right and what is wrong.","notes":"","source":{"title":"Core Book","pages":""},"key":"descriptor-principal.cazador","category":"hunter","owner":"babai-the-judge"},"flags":{"broken-tales":{"contentKey":"descriptor-principal.cazador.babai.the.judge","ownerKey":"hunter.babai.the.judge","descriptorRole":"principal-descriptor","contentSort":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Babai el Juez - descriptor-principal.cazador","system":{"description":"<p>Tras años de honorable servicio como inquisidor de estado de la República de Venecia, mi cuerpo y mi espíritu han sufrido una rara mutación y ahora el miedo me es desconocido. La gente siempre me ha llamado el hombre del saco, temiendo la justicia que representaba. Quizá mi propia carencia de miedo me hacía aún más aterrador a los ojos de los mortales. La Orden me ha encomendado una nueva misión porque, incluso en la lucha contra la oscuridad, alguien tiene que estar preparado para juzgar lo que está bien y lo que está mal.</p>"}}},"embeddedSource":"hunter-descriptors-canon","sequence":0,"ownerName":"Babai the Judge","ownerNameEs":"Babai el Juez","key":"descriptor-principal.cazador"}},"folder":"01rery4l01en0umi","sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"effects":[],"_id":"7bdb2b08e4b8e7e3"}
{"name":"Babai the Judge - descriptor1-don1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01rery4l01en0umi","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Babai the Judge","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.babai-the-judge","ownerKey":"cazador.babai-the-judge","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Babai el Juez - descriptor1-don1","system":{"description":"<p>Se me da bien comprender, evaluar y captar todos los detalles ocultos, razón por la que la Orden me quería como juez. Soy frío, metódico y no soporto que los planes cambien bruscamente.</p>","positive":"<p>Se me da bien comprender, evaluar y captar todos los detalles ocultos, razón por la que la Orden me quería como juez. Soy frío, metódico y no soporto que los planes cambien bruscamente.</p>"},"description":"<p>Se me da bien comprender, evaluar y captar todos los detalles ocultos, razón por la que la Orden me quería como <br>juez. Soy frío, metódico y no soporto que los planes cambien <br>bruscamente.</p>"}},"ownerName":"Babai the Judge","ownerNameEs":"Babai el Juez","key":"descriptor1-don1.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"I am good at understanding, evaluating, and grasping every hidden detail, which is why the Order wanted me as a judge. I am cold, methodical, and cannot stand when plans change abruptly.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 14.","positive":"I am good at understanding, evaluating, and grasping every hidden detail, which is why the Order wanted me as a judge. I am cold, methodical, and cannot stand when plans change abruptly.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"babai-the-judge","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.cazador"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"577ac50fbc843e5c"}
{"name":"Babai the Judge - descriptor2-don2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01rery4l01en0umi","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Babai the Judge","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.babai-the-judge","ownerKey":"cazador.babai-the-judge","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Babai el Juez - descriptor2-don2","system":{"description":"<p>Mi cuerpo está hecho de pura sombra y puedo volverme intangible durante breves instantes. Odio la luz del sol y no puedo concentrarme bien cuando no estoy rodeado de una sombra reconfortante.</p>","positive":"<p>Mi cuerpo está hecho de pura sombra y puedo volverme intangible durante breves instantes. Odio la luz del sol y no puedo concentrarme bien cuando no estoy rodeado de una sombra reconfortante.</p>"},"description":"<p>Mi cuerpo está hecho de pura sombra y puedo volverme <br>intangible durante breves instantes. Odio la luz del sol y no <br>puedo concentrarme bien cuando no estoy rodeado de una <br>sombra reconfortante.</p>"}},"ownerName":"Babai the Judge","ownerNameEs":"Babai el Juez","key":"descriptor2-don2.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"My body is made of pure shadow and I can become intangible for brief moments. I hate sunlight and cannot properly focus when not surrounded by a comforting shadow.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 14.","positive":"My body is made of pure shadow and I can become intangible for brief moments. I hate sunlight and cannot properly focus when not surrounded by a comforting shadow.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"babai-the-judge","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.cazador"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"2217c2bdbadd3e00"}
{"name":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name - descriptor-darkego.cazador","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01s7446m01mtt1jh","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","ownerKey":"cazador.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"system":{"description":"<p>Como artista he viajado a muchos lugares y conozco infinidad de mitos y leyendas. Tengo hambre de conocimiento y me fascina todo lo que ignoro.</p>","positive":"<p>Como artista he viajado a muchos lugares y conozco infinidad de mitos y leyendas. Tengo hambre de conocimiento y me fascina todo lo que ignoro.</p>"},"name":"El Asombroso Flautista sin Nombre - descriptor-darkego.cazador","description":"<p>Como artista he viajado a muchos lugares y conozco infinidad <br>de mitos y leyendas. Tengo hambre de conocimiento y me fascina <br>todo lo que ignoro.</p>"}},"ownerName":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","ownerNameEs":"El Asombroso Flautista sin Nombre","key":"descriptor-darkego.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"As an artist I have traveled to many places and I know many myths and legends. I’m hungry for knowledge and I’m fascinated by everything I don’t know.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 8.","positive":"As an artist I have traveled to many places and I know many myths and legends. I’m hungry for knowledge and I’m fascinated by everything I don’t know.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.cazador"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"93bc0a69928ddb63"}
{"name":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name - descriptor-principal.cazador","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","system":{"description":"I have always made my art my reason for living. I can play so skillfully that it might as well be magic. I have learned to use the power of music to reach into the souls of both humans and animals. Unfortunately, I have lost count of the number of times I have performed dishonorable acts while pursuing the perfect melody. Having been guilty of various crimes and having taken revenge on those who mocked my sincere love for music, I serenely waited for my execution. The Order freed me in exchange for a promise to serve them and put my skills to work in the fight against Darkness. It was in the darkest moments that I glimpsed the perfect melody, so perhaps as a Hunter, I can find it and make it my own.","notes":"","source":{"title":"Core Book","pages":""},"key":"descriptor-principal.cazador","category":"hunter","owner":"the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name"},"flags":{"broken-tales":{"contentKey":"descriptor-principal.cazador.the.astonishing.pied.piper.without.a.name","ownerKey":"hunter.the.astonishing.pied.piper.without.a.name","descriptorRole":"principal-descriptor","contentSort":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"El Asombroso Flautista sin Nombre - descriptor-principal.cazador","system":{"description":"<p>Con mi flauta puedo tocar cualquier melodía y llegar al corazón de los seres vivos. El arte necesita tiempo para expresarse.</p>"}}},"embeddedSource":"hunter-descriptors-canon","sequence":0,"ownerName":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","ownerNameEs":"El Asombroso Flautista sin Nombre","key":"descriptor-principal.cazador"}},"folder":"01s7446m01mtt1jh","sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"effects":[],"_id":"8c0e044207235917"}
{"name":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name - descriptor1-don1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01s7446m01mtt1jh","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","ownerKey":"cazador.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"system":{"description":"<p>Con mi flauta puedo tocar cualquier melodía y llegar al corazón de los seres vivos. El arte necesita tiempo para expresarse.</p>","positive":"<p>Con mi flauta puedo tocar cualquier melodía y llegar al corazón de los seres vivos. El arte necesita tiempo para expresarse.</p>"},"name":"El Asombroso Flautista sin Nombre - descriptor1-don1","description":"<p>Con mi flauta puedo tocar cualquier melodía y llegar al corazón de los seres vivos. El arte necesita tiempo para expresarse.</p>"}},"ownerName":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","ownerNameEs":"El Asombroso Flautista sin Nombre","key":"descriptor1-don1.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"With my pipe I can play any melody and touch the hearts of living beings. Art needs time to express itself.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 8.","positive":"With my pipe I can play any melody and touch the hearts of living beings. Art needs time to express itself.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.cazador"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"faba47cbe5e62849"}
{"name":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name - descriptor2-don2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01s7446m01mtt1jh","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","ownerKey":"cazador.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"system":{"description":"<p>Soy acróbata y músico. Mi talento es incomparable y la Orden me ha elegido por mi capacidad para captar la atención de la gente y estimular sus emociones. Cuando me invade la inspiración artística, me alejo totalmente de la realidad.</p>","positive":"<p>Soy acróbata y músico. Mi talento es incomparable y la Orden me ha elegido por mi capacidad para captar la atención de la gente y estimular sus emociones. Cuando me invade la inspiración artística, me alejo totalmente de la realidad.</p>"},"name":"El Asombroso Flautista sin Nombre - descriptor2-don2","description":"<p>Soy acróbata y músico. Mi talento es incomparable y la Orden <br>me ha elegido por mi capacidad para captar la atención de la <br>gente y estimular sus emociones. Cuando me invade la inspiración artística, me alejo totalmente de la realidad.</p>"}},"ownerName":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","ownerNameEs":"El Asombroso Flautista sin Nombre","key":"descriptor2-don2.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"I am a skilled acrobat and musician. My talent is unrivaled and the Order has chosen me for my ability to capture people’s attention and stimulate their emotions. When I am in the grip of artistic inspiration, I am totally divorced from reality.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 8.","positive":"I am a skilled acrobat and musician. My talent is unrivaled and the Order has chosen me for my ability to capture people’s attention and stimulate their emotions. When I am in the grip of artistic inspiration, I am totally divorced from reality.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.cazador"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"1b655c399641f0f4"}
{"name":"The Immortal - descriptor-darkego.cazador","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"00alws4p00s3d0gi","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"TheImmortal","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.theimmortal","ownerKey":"cazador.theimmortal","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"El Inmortal - descriptor-darkego.cazador","system":{"description":"<p>Mi cuerpo no es más que una herramienta que puedo manipular a voluntad, mucho más allá de los límites humanos ordinarios. A pesar de mi aspecto viejo y demacrado, no siento ni fatiga ni dolor. Como los asuntos de la carne ya no me preocupan, valoro las cosas bellas y las obras de arte por encima de cualquier otra cosa.</p>","positive":"<p>Mi cuerpo no es más que una herramienta que puedo manipular a voluntad, mucho más allá de los límites humanos ordinarios. A pesar de mi aspecto viejo y demacrado, no siento ni fatiga ni dolor. Como los asuntos de la carne ya no me preocupan, valoro las cosas bellas y las obras de arte por encima de cualquier otra cosa.</p>"},"description":"<p>Mi cuerpo no es más que una herramienta que puedo manipular a voluntad, mucho más allá de los límites humanos ordinarios. A pesar de mi aspecto viejo y demacrado, no siento ni fatiga ni dolor. Como los asuntos de la carne ya no me preocupan, valoro las cosas bellas y las obras de arte por encima de cualquier otra cosa.</p>"}},"ownerName":"The Immortal","ownerNameEs":"El Inmortal","key":"descriptor-darkego.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"My body is but a tool which I can manipulate at will, far beyond common human limits. In spite of my old and emaciated appearance, I feel neither fatigue nor pain. With matters of the flesh no longer of concern, I value beautiful things and works of art above anything else.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 18.","positive":"My body is but a tool which I can manipulate at will, far beyond common human limits. In spite of my old and emaciated appearance, I feel neither fatigue nor pain. With matters of the flesh no longer of concern, I value beautiful things and works of art above anything else.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"the-immortal","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.cazador"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"ac7523fb4ba452c0"}
{"name":"The Immortal - descriptor-principal.cazador","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","system":{"description":"I am a sorcerer who has found the key to immortality. Long life has only whetted my appetite for power and in its pursuit, I have been stained by every sin. The secret behind my unending existence is that I have hidden my soul, removing it from my body. Unfortunately, the Order found its hiding place and now it is held beyond my reach in a fortified church, leaving me no choice but to submit to their commands. Guilty of one thousand and one crimes, the Order demands I balance each with one thousand and one acts of virtue. According to those foolish preachers, they are leading me down the path of redemption. In truth, the Order treats me as a servant, giving to me only the most thankless tasks, knowing that I can not be subdued by death. I remain humble and silent, waiting for the day when I will discover where they have hidden my soul. Then I will unleash my revenge and annihilate the entire Papacy...","notes":"","source":{"title":"Core Book","pages":""},"key":"descriptor-principal.cazador","category":"hunter","owner":"the-immortal"},"flags":{"broken-tales":{"contentKey":"descriptor-principal.cazador.the.immortal","ownerKey":"hunter.the.immortal","descriptorRole":"principal-descriptor","contentSort":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"El Inmortal - descriptor-principal.cazador","system":{"description":"<p>Soy un hechicero que ha encontrado la clave de la inmortalidad. La larga vida no ha hecho más que despertar mi apetito de poder y, en su búsqueda, me he manchado con todos los pecados. El secreto que se oculta tras mi interminable existencia es que he escondido mi alma, separándola de mi cuerpo. Por desgracia, la Orden encontró su escondite y ahora está retenida fuera de mi alcance en una iglesia fortificada, sin dejarme otra opción que someterme a sus órdenes. Culpable de mil y un crímenes, la Orden exige que compense cada uno con mil y un actos de virtud. Según esos necios predicadores, me están guiando por el camino de la redención. En realidad, la Orden me trata como a un sirviente, dándome solo las tareas más ingratas, sabiendo que no puedo ser sometido por la muerte. Permanezco humilde y en silencio, esperando el día en que descubra dónde han escondido mi alma. Entonces desataré mi venganza y aniquilaré a todo el Papado...</p>"}}},"embeddedSource":"hunter-descriptors-canon","sequence":0,"ownerName":"The Immortal","ownerNameEs":"El Inmortal","key":"descriptor-principal.cazador"}},"folder":"00alws4p00s3d0gi","sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"effects":[],"_id":"96dda7b2be09647e"}
{"name":"The Immortal - descriptor1-don1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"00alws4p00s3d0gi","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"TheImmortal","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.theimmortal","ownerKey":"cazador.theimmortal","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"El Inmortal - descriptor1-don1","system":{"description":"<p>Poseo conocimientos y sabiduría extraídos de siglos de existencia, que puedo evocar cuando es necesario. A menudo me pierdo en los recuerdos de mis glorias pasadas, olvidándome del mundo que me rodea.</p>","positive":"<p>Poseo conocimientos y sabiduría extraídos de siglos de existencia, que puedo evocar cuando es necesario. A menudo me pierdo en los recuerdos de mis glorias pasadas, olvidándome del mundo que me rodea.</p>"},"description":"<p>Poseo conocimientos y sabiduría extraídos de siglos de <br>existencia, que puedo evocar cuando es necesario. A <br>menudo me pierdo en los recuerdos de mis glorias pasadas, olvidándome del mundo que me rodea.</p>"}},"ownerName":"The Immortal","ownerNameEs":"El Inmortal","key":"descriptor1-don1.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"I have knowledge and wisdom drawn from centuries of existence, which I can conjure to mind when needed. I often get lost in the memories of my past glories, forgetting about the world around me.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 18.","positive":"I have knowledge and wisdom drawn from centuries of existence, which I can conjure to mind when needed. I often get lost in the memories of my past glories, forgetting about the world around me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"the-immortal","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.cazador"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"3e0f500e82bbf640"}
{"name":"The Immortal - descriptor2-don2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"00alws4p00s3d0gi","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"TheImmortal","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.theimmortal","ownerKey":"cazador.theimmortal","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"El Inmortal - descriptor2-don2","system":{"description":"<p>Aunque odio admitirlo, con el tiempo he empezado a sentir cierto placer al hacer buenas obras.</p>","positive":"<p>Aunque odio admitirlo, con el tiempo he empezado a sentir cierto placer al hacer buenas obras.</p>"},"description":"<p>Aunque odio admitirlo, con el tiempo he empezado a <br>sentir cierto placer al hacer buenas obras.</p>"}},"ownerName":"The Immortal","ownerNameEs":"El Inmortal","key":"descriptor2-don2.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"The Order uses my powers for their own purposes and I have had to become skilled at understanding and supporting the needs of my allies as a result. Although I hate to admit it, over time I have begun to take some pleasure in doing good deeds.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 18.","positive":"The Order uses my powers for their own purposes and I have had to become skilled at understanding and supporting the needs of my allies as a result. Although I hate to admit it, over time I have begun to take some pleasure in doing good deeds.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"the-immortal","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.cazador"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"b9f23a9a388cd425"}
{"name":"Garou the Old Wolf - descriptor-darkego.cazador","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"000sp9z9003an7ie","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Garou the Old Wolf","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.garou-the-old-wolf","ownerKey":"cazador.garou-the-old-wolf","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Garou el Viejo Lobo - descriptor-darkego.cazador","system":{"description":"<p>Soy más feroz y poderoso que cualquier humano y mis colmillos pueden atravesar incluso el metal. Mi orgulloso espíritu de lobo lo es todo para mí.</p>"},"description":"<p>Soy más feroz y poderoso que cualquier humano y mis colmillos <br>pueden atravesar incluso el metal. Mi orgulloso espíritu de lobo <br>lo es todo para mí.</p>"}},"ownerName":"Garou the Old Wolf","ownerNameEs":"Garou el Viejo Lobo","key":"descriptor-darkego.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"I am fiercer and more powerful than any human and my fangs can pierce even metal. My proud wolf spirit is everything to me.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 6.","positive":"I am fiercer and more powerful than any human and my fangs can pierce even metal. My proud wolf spirit is everything to me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"garou-the-old-wolf","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.cazador"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"314d9fa5a8112062"}
{"name":"Garou the Old Wolf - descriptor-principal.cazador","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","system":{"description":"I am a mountain wolf and far more cunning than the stupid villagers who tremble at the mere sight of me. I have lived proudly at the head of my pack, leading a thousand raids and eating succulent, tender morsels of human flesh. But I am not so old I cannot face those who hate me the most, though I may be hunted and reviled. Now that I’m part of the Order, I use my strength to defend the weak hunters who are my companions, knowing that with a single bite I could end their insignificant lives.","notes":"","source":{"title":"Core Book","pages":""},"key":"descriptor-principal.cazador","category":"hunter","owner":"garou-the-old-wolf"},"flags":{"broken-tales":{"contentKey":"descriptor-principal.cazador.garou.the.old.wolf","ownerKey":"hunter.garou.the.old.wolf","descriptorRole":"principal-descriptor","contentSort":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Garou el Viejo Lobo - descriptor-principal.cazador","system":{"description":"<p>Soy un lobo de montaña, mucho más astuto que los estúpidos aldeanos que tiemblan solo con verme. He vivido orgulloso a la cabeza de mi manada, liderando mil incursiones y comiendo suculentos y tiernos bocados de carne humana. Pero no soy tan viejo como para no poder enfrentarme a los que más me odian, aunque me den caza y me vilipendien. Ahora que formo parte de la Orden, uso mi fuerza para defender a los débiles cazadores que son mis compañeros, sabiendo que con un solo mordisco podría acabar con sus insignificantes vidas.</p>"}}},"embeddedSource":"hunter-descriptors-canon","sequence":0,"ownerName":"Garou the Old Wolf","ownerNameEs":"Garou el Viejo Lobo","key":"descriptor-principal.cazador"}},"folder":"000sp9z9003an7ie","sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"effects":[],"_id":"8eee2f14b43c9094"}
{"name":"Garou the Old Wolf - descriptor1-don1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"000sp9z9003an7ie","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Garou the Old Wolf","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.garou-the-old-wolf","ownerKey":"cazador.garou-the-old-wolf","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Garou el Viejo Lobo - descriptor1-don1","system":{"description":"<p>Mis sentidos son infalibles. Nada puede escapar a mi olfato y por eso la Orden me utiliza como guardián. Odio los olores y los ruidos fuertes porque son como hierros candentes para mis agudos sentidos.</p>"},"description":"<p>Mis sentidos son infalibles. Nada puede escapar a mi olfato y <br>por eso la Orden me utiliza como guardián. Odio los olores <br>y los ruidos fuertes porque son como hierros candentes para <br>mis agudos sentidos.</p>"}},"ownerName":"Garou the Old Wolf","ownerNameEs":"Garou el Viejo Lobo","key":"descriptor1-don1.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"My senses are unfailing. Nothing can escape my sense of smell and that is why the Order uses me as a guardian. I hate strong smells and loud noises because they feel like burning irons to acute senses.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 6.","positive":"My senses are unfailing. Nothing can escape my sense of smell and that is why the Order uses me as a guardian. I hate strong smells and loud noises because they feel like burning irons to acute senses.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"garou-the-old-wolf","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.cazador"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"d5314d2d62345848"}
{"name":"Garou the Old Wolf - descriptor2-don2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"000sp9z9003an7ie","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Garou the Old Wolf","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.garou-the-old-wolf","ownerKey":"cazador.garou-the-old-wolf","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Garou el Viejo Lobo - descriptor2-don2","system":{"description":"<p>Un verdadero depredador sabe mostrarse como el más indefenso de los corderos. Yo sé cómo disfrazarme. Mi confianza es ilimitada y a menudo tiendo a subestimar el peligro, dispuesto a arriesgarme a todo por un sabroso bocado.</p>"},"description":"<p>Un verdadero depredador sabe mostrarse como el más indefenso de los corderos. Yo sé cómo disfrazarme. Mi confianza <br>es ilimitada y a menudo tiendo a subestimar el peligro, dispuesto a arriesgarme a todo por un sabroso bocado.</p>"}},"ownerName":"Garou the Old Wolf","ownerNameEs":"Garou el Viejo Lobo","key":"descriptor2-don2.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"A true predator knows how to appear as the most helpless of lambs. I know how to disguise myself. My confidence is boundless and I often tend to underestimate danger, ready to risk anything for a tasty bite.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 6.","positive":"A true predator knows how to appear as the most helpless of lambs. I know how to disguise myself. My confidence is boundless and I often tend to underestimate danger, ready to risk anything for a tasty bite.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"garou-the-old-wolf","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.cazador"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"a12b2ce68870c39c"}
{"name":"James the Swordsman - descriptor-darkego.cazador","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"00qilwez01s9oebo","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"James the Swordsman","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.james-the-swordsman","ownerKey":"cazador.james-the-swordsman","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Jaime el Espadachín - descriptor-darkego.cazador","system":{"description":"<p>Jaime el Espadachín Soy un hombre de mundo y ya nada puede sorprenderme. Nunca me cuestiono a mí mismo. Al fin y al cabo, soy el mejor en lo que hago.</p>","positive":"<p>Jaime el Espadachín Soy un hombre de mundo y ya nada puede sorprenderme. Nunca me cuestiono a mí mismo. Al fin y al cabo, soy el mejor en lo que hago.</p>"},"description":"<p>Jaime<br>el Espadachín<br>Soy un hombre de mundo y ya nada puede sorprenderme. Nunca me <br>cuestiono a mí mismo. Al fin y al cabo, soy el mejor en lo que <br>hago.</p>"}},"ownerName":"James the Swordsman","ownerNameEs":"Jaime el Espadachín","key":"descriptor-darkego.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"I am a man of the world and nothing can really surprise me anymore. I never question myself. After all, I’m the best at what I do.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 4.","positive":"I am a man of the world and nothing can really surprise me anymore. I never question myself. After all, I’m the best at what I do.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"james-the-swordsman","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.cazador"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241636,"modifiedTime":1783973241636,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"2ce85565bc7a7d17"}
{"name":"James the Swordsman - descriptor-principal.cazador","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","system":{"description":"I have been a lot of things in my life: ship captain, duellist of great renown, and lover of the most beautiful noblewomen. After years of successes and victories, a mysterious child defeated me with deception. This despicable boy led me into the lair of a dangerous beast and, after imprisoning me, left me to be eaten by the monster. I survived, though I lost a hand... I know for certain he who I seek is no human, and I joined the Order to hunt down the child I hate above all else, and thus have my revenge.","notes":"","source":{"title":"Core Book","pages":""},"key":"descriptor-principal.cazador","category":"hunter","owner":"james-the-swordsman"},"flags":{"broken-tales":{"contentKey":"descriptor-principal.cazador.james.the.swordsman","ownerKey":"hunter.james.the.swordsman","descriptorRole":"principal-descriptor","contentSort":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Jaime el Espadachín - descriptor-principal.cazador","system":{"description":"<p>He sido muchas cosas en mi vida: capitán de barco, duelista de gran renombre y amante de las nobles más bellas. Tras años de éxitos y victorias, un misterioso niño me derrotó con engaños. Este despreciable muchacho me condujo a la guarida de una peligrosa bestia y, tras apresarme, me dejó para que me devorara el monstruo. Sobreviví, aunque perdí una mano... Tengo la certeza de que aquel a quien busco no es humano, y me uní a la Orden para dar caza al niño que odio por encima de todo y así vengarme.</p>"}}},"embeddedSource":"hunter-descriptors-canon","sequence":0,"ownerName":"James the Swordsman","ownerNameEs":"Jaime el Espadachín","key":"descriptor-principal.cazador"}},"folder":"00qilwez01s9oebo","sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"effects":[],"_id":"1592f70234b4d78a"}
{"name":"James the Swordsman - descriptor1-don1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"00qilwez01s9oebo","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"James the Swordsman","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.james-the-swordsman","ownerKey":"cazador.james-the-swordsman","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Jaime el Espadachín - descriptor1-don1","system":{"description":"<p>Soy un hábil espadachín y tengo buenos modales, por lo que la Orden me considera un excelente candidato para moverme entre la alta sociedad. Me encanta deleitarme con la buena comida y la compañía alegre.</p>","positive":"<p>Soy un hábil espadachín y tengo buenos modales, por lo que la Orden me considera un excelente candidato para moverme entre la alta sociedad. Me encanta deleitarme con la buena comida y la compañía alegre.</p>"},"description":"<p>Soy un hábil espadachín y tengo buenos modales, por lo que la <br>Orden me considera un excelente candidato para moverme entre <br>la alta sociedad. Me encanta deleitarme con la buena comida y la <br>compañía alegre.</p>"}},"ownerName":"James the Swordsman","ownerNameEs":"Jaime el Espadachín","key":"descriptor1-don1.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"I am a skilled swordsman and possess fine manners, which is why the Order considers me an excellent candidate to move among High Society. I love indulging in good food and dissolute company.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 4.","positive":"I am a skilled swordsman and possess fine manners, which is why the Order considers me an excellent candidate to move among High Society. I love indulging in good food and dissolute company.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"james-the-swordsman","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.cazador"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241636,"modifiedTime":1783973241636,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"1221197948d6601c"}
{"name":"James the Swordsman - descriptor2-don2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"00qilwez01s9oebo","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"James the Swordsman","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.james-the-swordsman","ownerKey":"cazador.james-the-swordsman","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Jaime el Espadachín - descriptor2-don2","system":{"description":"<p>He aprendido a enfrentarme a monstruos y aberraciones sin dejarme intimidar. La Bestia me sigue el rastro porque, habiendo probado mi carne, ya no puede prescindir de ella...</p>","positive":"<p>He aprendido a enfrentarme a monstruos y aberraciones sin dejarme intimidar. La Bestia me sigue el rastro porque, habiendo probado mi carne, ya no puede prescindir de ella...</p>"},"description":"<p>He aprendido a enfrentarme a monstruos y aberraciones sin dejarme intimidar. La Bestia me sigue el rastro porque, habiendo <br>probado mi carne, ya no puede prescindir de ella...</p>"}},"ownerName":"James the Swordsman","ownerNameEs":"Jaime el Espadachín","key":"descriptor2-don2.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"I have learned to face monsters and aberrations without being intimidated. The Beast is on my trail because, having tasted my flesh, it can no longer do without it…","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 4.","positive":"I have learned to face monsters and aberrations without being intimidated. The Beast is on my trail because, having tasted my flesh, it can no longer do without it…","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"james-the-swordsman","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.cazador"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241636,"modifiedTime":1783973241636,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"b26bd11144437b65"}
{"name":"The Woman from the Woods - descriptor-darkego.cazador","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"00qjxzas00y9fqr5","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Woman from the Woods","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.the-woman-from-the-woods","ownerKey":"cazador.the-woman-from-the-woods","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"La Dama de los Bosques - descriptor-darkego.cazador","system":{"description":"<p>La Dama de los Bosques Me encanta la carne humana y puedo hacerme una idea de las personas solo con mirarlas. Me atraen sin remedio quienes tienen un rasgo físico particular que estimula mi apetito, como buen olor o piel aterciopelada.</p>","positive":"<p>La Dama de los Bosques Me encanta la carne humana y puedo hacerme una idea de las personas solo con mirarlas. Me atraen sin remedio quienes tienen un rasgo físico particular que estimula mi apetito, como buen olor o piel aterciopelada.</p>"},"description":"<p>La Dama<br>de los Bosques<br>Me encanta la carne humana y puedo hacerme una idea de <br>las personas solo con mirarlas. Me atraen sin remedio quienes tienen un rasgo físico particular que estimula mi apetito, <br>como buen olor o piel aterciopelada.</p>"}},"ownerName":"The Woman from the Woods","ownerNameEs":"La Dama de los Bosques","key":"descriptor-darkego.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"I love human flesh and can gain insight about people just looking at them. I am helplessly attracted to those who have a particular physical trait that stimulates my appetite, such as a good smell or velvety skin.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 16.","positive":"I love human flesh and can gain insight about people just looking at them. I am helplessly attracted to those who have a particular physical trait that stimulates my appetite, such as a good smell or velvety skin.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"the-woman-from-the-woods","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.cazador"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"e1e809853f886654"}
{"name":"The Woman from the Woods - descriptor-principal.cazador","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","system":{"description":"My memory is gone. The first thing I remember is the Order finding me, wandering in the woods naked and covered in blood. I possess extraordinary strength and a feral instinct, such that any civilized society ought to chain me like a monster. I know that in my past is a sin so great, my memory could not bear the weight of it. But, I want to remember and perhaps by serving the Order I will be able to do so. I have a natural soft spot for children, and I can’t stand to see them get hurt. The Order uses me as a weapon in the most serious matters when it is necessary to act decisively and demonstrate that a Hunter is a force to be reckoned with.","notes":"","source":{"title":"Core Book","pages":""},"key":"descriptor-principal.cazador","category":"hunter","owner":"the-woman-from-the-woods"},"flags":{"broken-tales":{"contentKey":"descriptor-principal.cazador.the.woman.from.the.woods","ownerKey":"hunter.the.woman.from.the.woods","descriptorRole":"principal-descriptor","contentSort":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"La Dama de los Bosques - descriptor-principal.cazador","system":{"description":"<p>He perdido la memoria. Lo primero que recuerdo es a la Orden encontrándome, vagando por el bosque desnuda y cubierta de sangre. Tengo una fuerza extraordinaria y un instinto salvaje, tanto que cualquier sociedad civilizada debería encadenarme como a un monstruo. Sé que en mi pasado hay un pecado tan grande, que mi memoria no podría soportar su peso. Pero quiero recordar y quizá sirviendo a la Orden pueda hacerlo. Tengo una debilidad natural por los niños y no soporto ver cómo les hacen daño. La Orden me utiliza como arma en los asuntos más graves, cuando es necesario actuar con decisión y demostrar que un Cazador es una fuerza a tener en cuenta.</p>"}}},"embeddedSource":"hunter-descriptors-canon","sequence":0,"ownerName":"The Woman from the Woods","ownerNameEs":"La Dama de los Bosques","key":"descriptor-principal.cazador"}},"folder":"00qjxzas00y9fqr5","sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"effects":[],"_id":"605f970c90630c4b"}
{"name":"The Woman from the Woods - descriptor1-don1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"00qjxzas00y9fqr5","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Woman from the Woods","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.the-woman-from-the-woods","ownerKey":"cazador.the-woman-from-the-woods","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"La Dama de los Bosques - descriptor1-don1","system":{"description":"<p>Soy increíblemente fuerte. A pesar de mi aspecto menudo, soy más dura que el más robusto de los hombres. Me cuesta controlar mi fuerza y a menudo acabo destrozando cosas sin querer.</p>","positive":"<p>Soy increíblemente fuerte. A pesar de mi aspecto menudo, soy más dura que el más robusto de los hombres. Me cuesta controlar mi fuerza y a menudo acabo destrozando cosas sin querer.</p>"},"description":"<p>Soy increíblemente fuerte. A pesar de mi aspecto menudo, soy más <br>dura que el más robusto de los hombres. Me cuesta controlar mi <br>fuerza y a menudo acabo destrozando cosas sin querer.</p>"}},"ownerName":"The Woman from the Woods","ownerNameEs":"La Dama de los Bosques","key":"descriptor1-don1.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"I am incredibly strong. Despite my petite looks, I am tougher than the sturdiest of men. I struggle to control my strength and often end up damaging things unintentionally.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 16.","positive":"I am incredibly strong. Despite my petite looks, I am tougher than the sturdiest of men. I struggle to control my strength and often end up damaging things unintentionally.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"the-woman-from-the-woods","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.cazador"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"61cf2af40bb988a6"}
{"name":"The Woman from the Woods - descriptor2-don2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"00qjxzas00y9fqr5","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Woman from the Woods","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.the-woman-from-the-woods","ownerKey":"cazador.the-woman-from-the-woods","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"La Dama de los Bosques - descriptor2-don2","system":{"description":"<p>A veces manifiesto extrañas aptitudes, herencia de un pasado que ya no recuerdo. Pero, cuando lo necesito, el mundo que me rodea se amolda para protegerme y cobijarme. Odio salir a la luz y ser el centro de atención.</p>","positive":"<p>A veces manifiesto extrañas aptitudes, herencia de un pasado que ya no recuerdo. Pero, cuando lo necesito, el mundo que me rodea se amolda para protegerme y cobijarme. Odio salir a la luz y ser el centro de atención.</p>"},"description":"<p>A veces manifiesto extrañas aptitudes, herencia de un pasado que <br>ya no recuerdo. Pero, cuando lo necesito, el mundo que me rodea <br>se amolda para protegerme y cobijarme. Odio salir a la luz y ser <br>el centro de atención.</p>"}},"ownerName":"The Woman from the Woods","ownerNameEs":"La Dama de los Bosques","key":"descriptor2-don2.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"Sometimes I manifest strange abilities, the legacy of a past that I no longer remember. But, when I need it, the world around me shapes itself to protect and shelter me. I hate being out in the open and being the center of attention.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 16.","positive":"Sometimes I manifest strange abilities, the legacy of a past that I no longer remember. But, when I need it, the world around me shapes itself to protect and shelter me. I hate being out in the open and being the center of attention.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"the-woman-from-the-woods","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.cazador"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"f6b3c250abe46240"}
{"name":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat - descriptor-principal.cazador","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","system":{"description":"We are two boys who survived and thrived on the street through trickery and deceit. Unfortunately, we made a terrible mistake by choosing a weird old lady as a mark. She turned out to be a goddamn witch. The witch cursed us… And from that day on, every twelve hours, one becomes a Fox and the other a Cat. Bound by this spell, we found a way to make a lot of money, deceiving stupid nobles and rich merchants. The Order has noticed us and taken us under its wing, with the promise of breaking the curse that afflicts us.","notes":"","source":{"title":"Core Book","pages":""},"key":"descriptor-principal.cazador","category":"hunter","owner":"cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat"},"flags":{"broken-tales":{"contentKey":"descriptor-principal.cazador.cunning.machiavelli.the.fox.and.sly.bischeri.the.cat","ownerKey":"hunter.cunning.machiavelli.the.fox.and.sly.bischeri.the.cat","descriptorRole":"principal-descriptor","contentSort":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Machiavelli el Zorro Astuto y Bischeri el Gato Malicioso - descriptor-principal.cazador","system":{"description":"Somos dos chicos que han sobrevivido y prosperado en las calles por medio del truco y el engaño. Por desgracia, cometimos un terrible error: mentimos a quien no debíamos y ahora pagamos las consecuencias sirviendo a la Orden. Uno de nosotros camina de noche como Astuto, el otro durante el día como Malicioso, y cuando la luz cambia también cambia quién lleva el cuerpo. Estamos condenados a compartir una misma vida, pero esa maldición también nos vuelve inseparables."}}},"embeddedSource":"hunter-descriptors-canon","sequence":0,"ownerName":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","ownerNameEs":"Machiavelli el Zorro Astuto y Bischeri el Gato Malicioso","key":"descriptor-principal.cazador"}},"folder":"00wswg3s01fth1uh","sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"effects":[],"_id":"880ea5a611e507db"}
{"name":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat - descriptor1-don1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"00wswg3s01fth1uh","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","ownerKey":"hunter.cunning.machiavelli.the.fox.and.sly.bischeri.the.cat","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Machiavelli el Zorro Astuto y Bischeri el Gato Malicioso - descriptor1-don1","system":{"description":"Tengo un talento natural para decir mentiras, el cual la Orden usa para su beneficio. A pesar de mis orígenes, sé mucho sobre muchas cosas porque mentir requiere planificación y preparación."}}},"ownerName":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","ownerNameEs":"Machiavelli el Zorro Astuto y Bischeri el Gato Malicioso","key":"descriptor1-don1.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"Cunning's Descriptor: I have a natural talent for telling lies, which the Order often uses to its advantage. Despite my origins, I know a great deal about many things because lying requires planning and preparation.","notes":"See bt-cb-foxcat-sheet-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 2.","positive":"Cunning's Descriptor: I have a natural talent for telling lies, which the Order often uses to its advantage. Despite my origins, I know a great deal about many things because lying requires planning and preparation.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.cazador"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"731d29f291fbfbec"}
{"name":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat - descriptor2-don2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"00wswg3s01fth1uh","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","ownerKey":"hunter.cunning.machiavelli.the.fox.and.sly.bischeri.the.cat","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Machiavelli el Zorro Astuto y Bischeri el Gato Malicioso - descriptor2-don2","system":{"description":"Una vida en el camino me enseñó a ser un ladrón talentoso, por lo que la Orden me usa para robar objetos importantes. Que cada uno se valga por sí mismo es mi lema."}}},"ownerName":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","ownerNameEs":"Machiavelli el Zorro Astuto y Bischeri el Gato Malicioso","key":"descriptor2-don2.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"Sly's Descriptor: A life on the road has taught me to be a skilled thief. Everyone for themselves is my motto.","notes":"See bt-cb-foxcat-sheet-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 2.","positive":"Sly's Descriptor: A life on the road has taught me to be a skilled thief. Everyone for themselves is my motto.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.cazador"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"00cff9f75db6d475"}
{"name":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat - descriptor3-don3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"00wswg3s01fth1uh","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor3-don3.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","ownerKey":"hunter.cunning.machiavelli.the.fox.and.sly.bischeri.the.cat","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":3,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Machiavelli el Zorro Astuto y Bischeri el Gato Malicioso - descriptor3-don3","system":{"description":"No me detendré ante nada para obtener lo que quiero, y solo me toma unos segundos evaluar lo que está pasando y cómo puedo aprovecharlo para mi beneficio. Malicioso y yo somos prácticamente inseparables."}}},"ownerName":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","ownerNameEs":"Machiavelli el Zorro Astuto y Bischeri el Gato Malicioso","key":"descriptor3-don3.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"Common Descriptor: I will stop at nothing to get what I want, and it only takes me a few seconds to evaluate what is happening and find the right way to take advantage of it. I hate acting alone because there's no one to take the blame.","notes":"See bt-cb-foxcat-sheet-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 2.","positive":"Common Descriptor: I will stop at nothing to get what I want, and it only takes me a few seconds to evaluate what is happening and find the right way to take advantage of it. I hate acting alone because there's no one to take the blame.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor3-don3.cazador"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"27737dc51dcaba1e"}
{"name":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat - descriptor-darkego.cazador","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"00wswg3s01fth1uh","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","ownerKey":"hunter.cunning.machiavelli.the.fox.and.sly.bischeri.the.cat","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":4,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Machiavelli el Zorro Astuto y Bischeri el Gato Malicioso - descriptor-darkego.cazador","system":{"description":"Nos guste o no, estamos atados por magia. Cada uno ve lo que el otro puede ver y, gracias a esto, podemos trabajar juntos de manera perfecta. Somos dos y uno al mismo tiempo, y esa maldición es lo único que nos mantiene vivos."}}},"ownerName":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","ownerNameEs":"Machiavelli el Zorro Astuto y Bischeri el Gato Malicioso","key":"descriptor-darkego.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"Like it or not, we are bound by magic. We can share thoughts, each see what the other sees, and thanks to this we can work together to cheat others. Whoever is in animal form hates not being able to communicate and often annoys the other out of spite.","notes":"See bt-cb-foxcat-sheet-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 2.","positive":"Like it or not, we are bound by magic. We can share thoughts, each see what the other sees, and thanks to this we can work together to cheat others. Whoever is in animal form hates not being able to communicate and often annoys the other out of spite.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.cazador"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"b148b4b61910f2e7"}
{"name":"Marina the Sea Explorer - descriptor-darkego.cazador","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"0021f61c011tobuj","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Marina the Sea Explorer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.marina-the-sea-explorer","ownerKey":"cazador.marina-the-sea-explorer","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Marina la Exploradora del Mar - descriptor-darkego.cazador","system":{"description":"<p>Tengo una enorme colección de reliquias y tesoros mágicos. Soy muy tacaña con mi colección y busco constantemente aumentar mi riqueza para poder recuperar mi libertad.</p>","positive":"<p>Tengo una enorme colección de reliquias y tesoros mágicos. Soy muy tacaña con mi colección y busco constantemente aumentar mi riqueza para poder recuperar mi libertad.</p>"},"description":"<p>Tengo una enorme colección de reliquias y tesoros mágicos. Soy muy <br>tacaña con mi colección y busco constantemente aumentar mi riqueza para poder recuperar mi libertad.</p>"}},"ownerName":"Marina the Sea Explorer","ownerNameEs":"Marina la Exploradora del Mar","key":"descriptor-darkego.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"I have a massive collection of magical relics and treasures. I am very stingy with my collection and constantly seeking to add to my wealth so I can redeem my freedom.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 20.","positive":"I have a massive collection of magical relics and treasures. I am very stingy with my collection and constantly seeking to add to my wealth so I can redeem my freedom.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"marina-the-sea-explorer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.cazador"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"4051d3f4bfc3c783"}
{"name":"Marina the Sea Explorer - descriptor-principal.cazador","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","system":{"description":"I am a traveler, and, over the years, I have visited every location known to man. Being a traveling merchant has allowed me to easily hide my talents as a witch from prying eyes. Year after year, I have accumulated all kinds of magical and mundane wealth. But the Order found me and forced me to sign the most one-sided contract of my entire career as a trader. Now I must put my skills and my charisma at the service of the Order, trying to earn as much as possible to redeem the enormous debt that they have made me incur through deceit.","notes":"","source":{"title":"Core Book","pages":""},"key":"descriptor-principal.cazador","category":"hunter","owner":"marina-the-sea-explorer"},"flags":{"broken-tales":{"contentKey":"descriptor-principal.cazador.marina.the.sea.explorer","ownerKey":"hunter.marina.the.sea.explorer","descriptorRole":"principal-descriptor","contentSort":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Marina la Exploradora del Mar - descriptor-principal.cazador","system":{"description":"<p>Soy una viajera y, a lo largo de los años, he visitado todos los lugares conocidos por el hombre. Ser una mercader ambulante me ha permitido ocultar fácilmente de miradas indiscretas mi talento como bruja. Año tras año, he acumulado todo tipo de riquezas mágicas y mundanas. Pero la Orden me encontró y me obligó a firmar el contrato más unilateral de toda mi carrera como comerciante. Ahora debo poner mis habilidades y mi carisma al servicio de la Orden, intentando ganar lo máximo posible para redimir la enorme deuda que me han hecho contraer con engaños. Tengo una enorme colección de reliquias y tesoros mágicos. Soy muy tacaña con mi colección y busco constantemente aumentar mi riqueza para poder recuperar mi libertad.</p>"}}},"embeddedSource":"hunter-descriptors-canon","sequence":0,"ownerName":"Marina the Sea Explorer","ownerNameEs":"Marina la Exploradora del Mar","key":"descriptor-principal.cazador"}},"folder":"0021f61c011tobuj","sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"effects":[],"_id":"e24177697064a66b"}
{"name":"Marina the Sea Explorer - descriptor1-don1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"0021f61c011tobuj","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Marina the Sea Explorer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.marina-the-sea-explorer","ownerKey":"cazador.marina-the-sea-explorer","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Marina la Exploradora del Mar - descriptor1-don1","system":{"description":"<p>Soy una bruja del mar y, como tal, tengo el poder de moldear el agua y moverla a voluntad. Odio los lugares cerrados, aislados de la presencia de mi amado mar.</p>","positive":"<p>Soy una bruja del mar y, como tal, tengo el poder de moldear el agua y moverla a voluntad. Odio los lugares cerrados, aislados de la presencia de mi amado mar.</p>"},"description":"<p>Soy una bruja del mar y, como tal, tengo el poder de moldear <br>el agua y moverla a voluntad. Odio los lugares cerrados, aislados de la presencia de mi amado mar.</p>"}},"ownerName":"Marina the Sea Explorer","ownerNameEs":"Marina la Exploradora del Mar","key":"descriptor1-don1.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"I am a sea witch, and as such, I have the power to shape water and move it at will. I hate enclosed places, cut off from the presence of my beloved sea.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 20.","positive":"I am a sea witch, and as such, I have the power to shape water and move it at will. I hate enclosed places, cut off from the presence of my beloved sea.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"marina-the-sea-explorer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.cazador"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"81d39f480b65a68f"}
{"name":"Marina the Sea Explorer - descriptor2-don2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"0021f61c011tobuj","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Marina the Sea Explorer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.marina-the-sea-explorer","ownerKey":"cazador.marina-the-sea-explorer","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Marina la Exploradora del Mar - descriptor2-don2","system":{"description":"<p>Nadie conoce mi verdadera forma, que oculto bajo una apariencia de eterna juventud. Puedo cambiar de forma hasta cierto punto, sin dejar de ser humana. Me atraen irremediablemente todas las formas de belleza y a menudo me pierdo en su contemplación.</p>","positive":"<p>Nadie conoce mi verdadera forma, que oculto bajo una apariencia de eterna juventud. Puedo cambiar de forma hasta cierto punto, sin dejar de ser humana. Me atraen irremediablemente todas las formas de belleza y a menudo me pierdo en su contemplación.</p>"},"description":"<p>Nadie conoce mi verdadera forma, que oculto bajo una apariencia de eterna juventud. Puedo cambiar de forma hasta <br>cierto punto, sin dejar de ser humana. Me atraen irremediablemente todas las formas de belleza y a menudo me pierdo en <br>su contemplación.</p>"}},"ownerName":"Marina the Sea Explorer","ownerNameEs":"Marina la Exploradora del Mar","key":"descriptor2-don2.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"Nobody knows my true form, which I hide under an appearance of eternal youth. I can change shape to some extent, while still remaining in human form. I am hopelessly attracted to all forms of beauty and I often get lost in contemplating it.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 20.","positive":"Nobody knows my true form, which I hide under an appearance of eternal youth. I can change shape to some extent, while still remaining in human form. I am hopelessly attracted to all forms of beauty and I often get lost in contemplating it.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"marina-the-sea-explorer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.cazador"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"4d0d4d496787fc56"}
{"name":"Niklaus von Krampus - descriptor-darkego.cazador","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"010dnekx00ixx2cq","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Niklaus von Krampus","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.niklaus-von-krampus","ownerKey":"cazador.niklaus-von-krampus","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Niklaus von Krampus - descriptor-darkego.cazador","system":{"description":"<p>El demonio que hay en mí me otorga su poder, permitiéndome actuar con una fuerza y velocidad salvajes. No es fácil contener esta ferocidad y, a menudo, acabo hiriendo a alguien o destrozando cosas cuando no era mi intención.</p>","positive":"<p>El demonio que hay en mí me otorga su poder, permitiéndome actuar con una fuerza y velocidad salvajes. No es fácil contener esta ferocidad y, a menudo, acabo hiriendo a alguien o destrozando cosas cuando no era mi intención.</p>"},"description":"<p>El demonio que hay en mí me otorga su poder, permitiéndome actuar con <br>una fuerza y velocidad salvajes. No es fácil contener esta ferocidad y, a menudo, acabo hiriendo a alguien o destrozando cosas cuando no era mi intención.</p>"}},"ownerName":"Niklaus von Krampus","ownerNameEs":"Niklaus von Krampus","key":"descriptor-darkego.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"The demon in me grants me its power, allowing me to act with savage strength and speed. It is not easy to contain this ferocity and, often, I end up hurting or destroying things I did not wish to.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 22.","positive":"The demon in me grants me its power, allowing me to act with savage strength and speed. It is not easy to contain this ferocity and, often, I end up hurting or destroying things I did not wish to.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"niklaus-von-krampus","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.cazador"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"fb6a0082b977b676"}
{"name":"Niklaus von Krampus - descriptor-principal.cazador","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","system":{"description":"I am a devoted clergyman who has always dedicated his life to helping others. Over the years I have become a talented exorcist and this vocation of mine led me to the remote village of Borgo Maleanime. There, I fought a particularly insidious demon, who concealed itself among the ranks of a gang of young thugs who merely pretended to be demons to scare people. It was a tough fight, but I finally got the better of the fiend. Or so I thought. Something in the exorcism did not go as expected and now the demon dwells inside me, sowing fear and pain whenever it re-emerges. The Order welcomed me into its ranks as an exorcist and I gladly accepted this role, with the hope that the missions entrusted to me would allow me to find a way to rid myself, once and for all, of that which hides within me.","notes":"","source":{"title":"Core Book","pages":""},"key":"descriptor-principal.cazador","category":"hunter","owner":"niklaus-von-krampus"},"flags":{"broken-tales":{"contentKey":"descriptor-principal.cazador.niklaus.von.krampus","ownerKey":"hunter.niklaus.von.krampus","descriptorRole":"principal-descriptor","contentSort":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Niklaus von Krampus - descriptor-principal.cazador","system":{"description":"<p>Soy un clérigo devoto que siempre ha dedicado su vida a ayudar a los demás. Con los años me he convertido en un exorcista de talento y esta vocación mía me llevó al remoto pueblo de Borgo Maleanime. Allí luché contra un demonio especialmente insidioso, que se ocultaba entre las filas de una pandilla de jóvenes matones que solo fingían ser demonios para asustar a la gente. Fue un combate duro, pero finalmente conseguí vencer al demonio. O eso creía. Algo en el exorcismo no salió como esperaba y ahora el demonio habita en mi interior, sembrando el miedo y el dolor cada vez que reaparece. La Orden me acogió en sus filas como exorcista y acepté de buen grado este papel, con la esperanza de que las misiones que me encomendaran me permitieran encontrar la forma de librarme, de una vez por todas, de aquello que se esconde en mi interior.</p>"}}},"embeddedSource":"hunter-descriptors-canon","sequence":0,"ownerName":"Niklaus von Krampus","ownerNameEs":"Niklaus von Krampus","key":"descriptor-principal.cazador"}},"folder":"010dnekx00ixx2cq","sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"effects":[],"_id":"8bbb6958d1dca156"}
{"name":"Niklaus von Krampus - descriptor1-don1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"010dnekx00ixx2cq","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Niklaus von Krampus","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.niklaus-von-krampus","ownerKey":"cazador.niklaus-von-krampus","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Niklaus von Krampus - descriptor1-don1","system":{"description":"<p>Soy un experto exorcista. Sé identificar y combatir el mal mediante la oración y las artes sagradas. A pesar de lo que soy, odio los lugares sagrados y las manifestaciones de fe y religión, ya que hacen que se agite el demonio que llevo dentro.</p>","positive":"<p>Soy un experto exorcista. Sé identificar y combatir el mal mediante la oración y las artes sagradas. A pesar de lo que soy, odio los lugares sagrados y las manifestaciones de fe y religión, ya que hacen que se agite el demonio que llevo dentro.</p>"},"description":"<p>Soy un experto exorcista. Sé identificar y combatir el mal <br>mediante la oración y las artes sagradas. A pesar de lo <br>que soy, odio los lugares sagrados y las manifestaciones <br>de fe y religión, ya que hacen que se agite el demonio que <br>llevo dentro.</p>"}},"ownerName":"Niklaus von Krampus","ownerNameEs":"Niklaus von Krampus","key":"descriptor1-don1.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"I am a skilled exorcist. I know how to identify and fight evil through prayer and the sacred arts. Despite what I am, I hate holy places and manifestations of faith and religion, as they cause the demon inside me to stir.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 22.","positive":"I am a skilled exorcist. I know how to identify and fight evil through prayer and the sacred arts. Despite what I am, I hate holy places and manifestations of faith and religion, as they cause the demon inside me to stir.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"niklaus-von-krampus","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.cazador"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"4d6477899950b513"}
{"name":"Niklaus von Krampus - descriptor2-don2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"010dnekx00ixx2cq","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Niklaus von Krampus","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.niklaus-von-krampus","ownerKey":"cazador.niklaus-von-krampus","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Niklaus von Krampus - descriptor2-don2","system":{"description":"<p>Se me da bien comprender a la gente y ayudarla. Ahora, gracias al demonio que habita en mí, puedo incluso percibir el lado oscuro de las personas. Sin embargo, de vez en cuando, el demonio se apodera de mí y me hace comportarme de forma extraña ante la gente corriente.</p>","positive":"<p>Se me da bien comprender a la gente y ayudarla. Ahora, gracias al demonio que habita en mí, puedo incluso percibir el lado oscuro de las personas. Sin embargo, de vez en cuando, el demonio se apodera de mí y me hace comportarme de forma extraña ante la gente corriente.</p>"},"description":"<p>Se me da bien comprender a la gente y ayudarla. Ahora, <br>gracias al demonio que habita en mí, puedo incluso percibir el lado oscuro de las personas. Sin embargo, de vez <br>en cuando, el demonio se apodera de mí y me hace comportarme de forma extraña ante la gente corriente.</p>"}},"ownerName":"Niklaus von Krampus","ownerNameEs":"Niklaus von Krampus","key":"descriptor2-don2.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"I am good at understanding people and helping them. Now, thanks to the demon that dwells in me, I can even perceive the dark side of people. Every so often, however, the demon takes over, making me behave strangely in front of ordinary people.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 22.","positive":"I am good at understanding people and helping them. Now, thanks to the demon that dwells in me, I can even perceive the dark side of people. Every so often, however, the demon takes over, making me behave strangely in front of ordinary people.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"niklaus-von-krampus","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.cazador"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"2d62567f4c82120d"}
{"name":"Regina the Thief of Hearts - descriptor-darkego.cazador","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"00erjoh1016tw79q","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.regina-the-thief-of-hearts","ownerKey":"cazador.regina-the-thief-of-hearts","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Regina la Ladrona de Corazones - descriptor-darkego.cazador","system":{"description":"<p>Tengo un encanto envidiable y me encanta arreglarme para encajar en el papel que he elegido. Incluso cuando intento contenerme, nunca paso desapercibida.</p>","positive":"<p>Tengo un encanto envidiable y me encanta arreglarme para encajar en el papel que he elegido. Incluso cuando intento contenerme, nunca paso desapercibida.</p>"},"description":"<p>Tengo un encanto envidiable y me encanta arreglarme para encajar <br>en el papel que he elegido. Incluso cuando intento contenerme, nunca <br>paso desapercibida.</p>"}},"ownerName":"Regina the Thief of Hearts","ownerNameEs":"Regina la Ladrona de Corazones","key":"descriptor-darkego.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"I have an enviable charm and love to dress up to fit the role I have chosen. Even when I try to restrain myself, I never go unnoticed.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 12.","positive":"I have an enviable charm and love to dress up to fit the role I have chosen. Even when I try to restrain myself, I never go unnoticed.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"regina-the-thief-of-hearts","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.cazador"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"8483af23898109aa"}
{"name":"Regina the Thief of Hearts - descriptor-principal.cazador","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","system":{"description":"I was born to be a leader and I have always surrounded myself with faithful followers ready to satisfy my every whim. Lacking the benefit of noble birth, the power I held was pried from the hands of those less deserving to wield it, no matter the cost. I ruled armies of thugs, and broke the hearts of both men and women. After each conquest, I set out in search of a bigger challenge. Because there is still so much out there that should be rightfully mine, I always want more. The Order has given me a new purpose, a new perspective, and new creatures to enslave.","notes":"","source":{"title":"Core Book","pages":""},"key":"descriptor-principal.cazador","category":"hunter","owner":"regina-the-thief-of-hearts"},"flags":{"broken-tales":{"contentKey":"descriptor-principal.cazador.regina.the.thief.of.hearts","ownerKey":"hunter.regina.the.thief.of.hearts","descriptorRole":"principal-descriptor","contentSort":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Regina la Ladrona de Corazones - descriptor-principal.cazador","system":{"description":"<p>Nací para ser líder y siempre me he rodeado de fieles seguidores dispuestos a satisfacer todos mis caprichos. Al carecer del beneficio de la nobleza de nacimiento, el poder que ostentaba lo arrebataba de las manos de quienes menos merecían ejercerlo, sin importar el coste. Goberné ejércitos de matones y rompí los corazones de hombres y mujeres. Tras cada conquista, partía en busca de un desafío mayor. Como todavía hay mucho ahí fuera que debería ser mío por derecho, siempre quiero más. La Orden me ha dado un nuevo propósito, una nueva perspectiva y nuevas criaturas a las que esclavizar. Tengo un encanto envidiable y me encanta arreglarme para encajar en el papel que he elegido. Incluso cuando intento contenerme, nunca paso desapercibida.</p>"}}},"embeddedSource":"hunter-descriptors-canon","sequence":0,"ownerName":"Regina the Thief of Hearts","ownerNameEs":"Regina la Ladrona de Corazones","key":"descriptor-principal.cazador"}},"folder":"00erjoh1016tw79q","sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"effects":[],"_id":"cb6ae4eaaf8d4421"}
{"name":"Regina the Thief of Hearts - descriptor1-don1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"00erjoh1016tw79q","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.regina-the-thief-of-hearts","ownerKey":"cazador.regina-the-thief-of-hearts","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Regina la Ladrona de Corazones - descriptor1-don1","system":{"description":"<p>Estoy decidida a conseguir lo que quiero, y nada se interpondrá en mi camino. Mataré, humillaré o conquistaré a cualquiera o cualquier cosa que se interponga entre mi objetivo y yo. Como puedes imaginar, ¡odio sinceramente que me digan que no!</p>","positive":"<p>Estoy decidida a conseguir lo que quiero, y nada se interpondrá en mi camino. Mataré, humillaré o conquistaré a cualquiera o cualquier cosa que se interponga entre mi objetivo y yo. Como puedes imaginar, ¡odio sinceramente que me digan que no!</p>"},"description":"<p>Estoy decidida a conseguir lo que quiero, y nada se interpondrá <br>en mi camino. Mataré, humillaré o conquistaré a cualquiera o <br>cualquier cosa que se interponga entre mi objetivo y yo. Como <br>puedes imaginar, ¡odio sinceramente que me digan que no!</p>"}},"ownerName":"Regina the Thief of Hearts","ownerNameEs":"Regina la Ladrona de Corazones","key":"descriptor1-don1.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"I am determined to get what I want, and nothing will get in my way. I will kill, humiliate, or conquer anything that stands between me and my objective. As you can imagine, I sincerely hate being told no!","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 12.","positive":"I am determined to get what I want, and nothing will get in my way. I will kill, humiliate, or conquer anything that stands between me and my objective. As you can imagine, I sincerely hate being told no!","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"regina-the-thief-of-hearts","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.cazador"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"bc1262286678309d"}
{"name":"Regina the Thief of Hearts - descriptor2-don2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"00erjoh1016tw79q","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.regina-the-thief-of-hearts","ownerKey":"cazador.regina-the-thief-of-hearts","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Regina la Ladrona de Corazones - descriptor2-don2","system":{"description":"<p>Gracias a mis contactos y a mi carisma, siempre tengo un as en la manga: seguidores dispuestos a ayudarme y aliados que me deben favores. Mantener un imperio de conexiones beneficiosas requiere compromiso y recursos.</p>","positive":"<p>Gracias a mis contactos y a mi carisma, siempre tengo un as en la manga: seguidores dispuestos a ayudarme y aliados que me deben favores. Mantener un imperio de conexiones beneficiosas requiere compromiso y recursos.</p>"},"description":"<p>Gracias a mis contactos y a mi carisma, siempre tengo un as <br>en la manga: seguidores dispuestos a ayudarme y aliados que <br>me deben favores. Mantener un imperio de conexiones beneficiosas requiere compromiso y recursos.</p>"}},"ownerName":"Regina the Thief of Hearts","ownerNameEs":"Regina la Ladrona de Corazones","key":"descriptor2-don2.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"Thanks to my contacts and charisma, I always have an ace up my sleeve: followers ready to help me and allies who owe me favors. Maintaining an empire of beneficial connections requires commitment and resources.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 12.","positive":"Thanks to my contacts and charisma, I always have an ace up my sleeve: followers ready to help me and allies who owe me favors. Maintaining an empire of beneficial connections requires commitment and resources.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"regina-the-thief-of-hearts","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.cazador"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"8684cf2fb60fe882"}
{"name":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer - descriptor-darkego.cazador","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01oli18b005h8knu","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","ownerKey":"cazador.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"San Jorge el Matadragones - descriptor-darkego.cazador","system":{"description":"<p>San Jorge el matadragones Soy un santo a los ojos de la gente corriente y ninguna puerta permanece cerrada para mí. Mi palabra es la de la propia Iglesia. Lo que digo no se pone en duda.</p>","positive":"<p>San Jorge el matadragones Soy un santo a los ojos de la gente corriente y ninguna puerta permanece cerrada para mí. Mi palabra es la de la propia Iglesia. Lo que digo no se pone en duda.</p>"},"description":"<p>San Jorge <br>el matadragones<br>Soy un santo a los ojos de la gente corriente y ninguna puerta per -<br>manece cerrada para mí. Mi palabra es la de la propia Iglesia. Lo que <br>digo no se pone en duda.</p>"}},"ownerName":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","ownerNameEs":"San Jorge el Matadragones","key":"descriptor-darkego.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"I am a saint in the eyes of ordinary people and no door remains closed for me. My word is that of the Church itself. What I say is not to be questioned.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 24.","positive":"I am a saint in the eyes of ordinary people and no door remains closed for me. My word is that of the Church itself. What I say is not to be questioned.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.cazador"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"a56ed26d7719f9e5"}
{"name":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer - descriptor-principal.cazador","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","system":{"description":"I am the most skilled and trusted agent of the Papacy and as such, it is my responsibility to make sure that the fight against darkness never falters. As a child, I fell into a river and almost drowned, but was saved by a creature that I later discovered was a dragon. When I grew up, I took holy vows and joined the Church. In doing so, I discovered that what I believed to be my savior was actually a creature of darkness, ready to steal my soul. I vowed to fight the darkness, suppressing the feeling of gratitude toward the dragon that saved me, which has always plagued me. Such weakness represents a crack through which evil could slither in. No mercy for monsters, no forgiveness for those who would join and serve the forces of evil.","notes":"","source":{"title":"Core Book","pages":""},"key":"descriptor-principal.cazador","category":"hunter","owner":"george-the-holy-dragon-slayer"},"flags":{"broken-tales":{"contentKey":"descriptor-principal.cazador.george.the.holy.dragon.slayer","ownerKey":"hunter.george.the.holy.dragon.slayer","descriptorRole":"principal-descriptor","contentSort":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"San Jorge el Matadragones - descriptor-principal.cazador","system":{"description":"<p>No hay piedad para los monstruos, ni perdón para los que se unen y sirven a las fuerzas del mal.</p>"}}},"embeddedSource":"hunter-descriptors-canon","sequence":0,"ownerName":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","ownerNameEs":"San Jorge el Matadragones","key":"descriptor-principal.cazador"}},"folder":"01oli18b005h8knu","sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"effects":[],"_id":"adc0fb87ee0e10ec"}
{"name":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer - descriptor1-don1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01oli18b005h8knu","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","ownerKey":"cazador.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"San Jorge el Matadragones - descriptor1-don1","system":{"description":"<p>He dedicado mi vida a matar monstruos y aberraciones, perfeccionando mi cuerpo y mi habilidad para ello. Mi estricta disciplina hace que rara vez me sienta inclinado a perdonar los errores de los demás.</p>","positive":"<p>He dedicado mi vida a matar monstruos y aberraciones, perfeccionando mi cuerpo y mi habilidad para ello. Mi estricta disciplina hace que rara vez me sienta inclinado a perdonar los errores de los demás.</p>"},"description":"<p>He dedicado mi vida a matar monstruos y aberraciones, perfeccionando mi cuerpo y mi habilidad para ello. <br>Mi estricta disciplina hace que rara vez me sienta inclinado a perdonar los errores de los demás.</p>"}},"ownerName":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","ownerNameEs":"San Jorge el Matadragones","key":"descriptor1-don1.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"I have dedicated my life to slaying monsters and aberrations, honing my body and my skill for that purpose. My strict discipline makes me rarely inclined to forgive the mistakes of others.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 24.","positive":"I have dedicated my life to slaying monsters and aberrations, honing my body and my skill for that purpose. My strict discipline makes me rarely inclined to forgive the mistakes of others.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.cazador"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"d72d1f263f0b257d"}
{"name":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer - descriptor2-don2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01oli18b005h8knu","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","ownerKey":"cazador.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"San Jorge el Matadragones - descriptor2-don2","system":{"description":"<p>He jurado erradicar todo el mal de este mundo y nada puede escapar a mi mirada inquisitiva. Odio todos los secretos, pues sé que la semilla del mal puede crecer dentro de cualquiera.</p>","positive":"<p>He jurado erradicar todo el mal de este mundo y nada puede escapar a mi mirada inquisitiva. Odio todos los secretos, pues sé que la semilla del mal puede crecer dentro de cualquiera.</p>"},"description":"<p>He jurado erradicar todo el mal de este mundo y nada <br>puede escapar a mi mirada inquisitiva. Odio todos los <br>secretos, pues sé que la semilla del mal puede crecer dentro de cualquiera.</p>"}},"ownerName":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","ownerNameEs":"San Jorge el Matadragones","key":"descriptor2-don2.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"I have vowed to eradicate all evil from this world and nothing can escape my inquisitive gaze. I hate all secrets, for I know that the seed of evil may grow within anyone.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 24.","positive":"I have vowed to eradicate all evil from this world and nothing can escape my inquisitive gaze. I hate all secrets, for I know that the seed of evil may grow within anyone.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.cazador"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"d1f90e6dd9a089f6"}
{"name":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey - descriptor-darkego.cazador","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01svescg01ulp26r","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","ownerKey":"cazador.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Sun Wukong el Mono Asombroso - descriptor-darkego.cazador","description":"<p></p>","system":{"description":"Mi esencia es mágica, y eso me vuelve resistente a los encantamientos que podrían atrapar a humanos necios. Mi presencia espiritual es imponente, y me cuesta ocultar lo que soy, especialmente cuando la rabia o el orgullo despiertan mi verdadera naturaleza."}}},"ownerName":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey","ownerNameEs":"Sun Wukong el Mono Asombroso","key":"descriptor-darkego.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"My essence is magical, and this makes me resistant to enchantments that might snare stupid humans. My spiritual presence is imposing, and I struggle to hide what I am, especially in the eyes of those accustomed to magic.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 26.","positive":"My essence is magical, and this makes me resistant to enchantments that might snare stupid humans. My spiritual presence is imposing, and I struggle to hide what I am, especially in the eyes of those accustomed to magic.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.cazador"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"d384b6c549ea2b1c"}
{"name":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey - descriptor-principal.cazador","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","system":{"description":"I have no memory of my life before my captivity, although I often dream of the forests and snow-capped peaks of my beloved China. I grew up as a circus animal at London’s Royal Circus but, deep within I carry the conviction that I am destined for something else. I rebelled by killing all my captors, fleeing across a vast and labyrinthine city. When the Order reached me, I thought it was the end, but the Hunters took me with them as their guardian and defender. The more I live as a Hunter, the closer I draw to transcendence. Now I am aware that, someday, I will discover who I really am.","notes":"","source":{"title":"Core Book","pages":""},"key":"descriptor-principal.cazador","category":"hunter","owner":"sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey"},"flags":{"broken-tales":{"contentKey":"descriptor-principal.cazador.sun.wukong.the.amazing.monkey","ownerKey":"hunter.sun.wukong.the.amazing.monkey","descriptorRole":"principal-descriptor","contentSort":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Sun Wukong el Mono Asombroso - descriptor-principal.cazador","system":{"description":"No recuerdo mi vida antes del cautiverio, aunque a menudo sueño con los bosques y las cumbres nevadas de mi amada China. Crecí como animal de circo en el Royal Circus de Londres, encadenado y obligado a obedecer. Ahora uso mi fuerza y mi agilidad para la Orden, aunque todavía lucho contra las cadenas invisibles que me enseñaron a aceptar."}}},"embeddedSource":"hunter-descriptors-canon","sequence":0,"ownerName":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey","ownerNameEs":"Sun Wukong el Mono Asombroso","key":"descriptor-principal.cazador"}},"folder":"01svescg01ulp26r","sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"effects":[],"_id":"576f595ea706c726"}
{"name":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey - descriptor1-don1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01svescg01ulp26r","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","ownerKey":"cazador.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Sun Wukong el Mono Asombroso - descriptor1-don1","system":{"description":"<p>Soy un guardián experto. Mi cuerpo es fuerte y robusto, mis sentidos agudos y alerta. Años de cautiverio me han vuelto sumiso, y lucho por no seguir todas las órdenes que me dan.</p>","positive":"<p>Soy un guardián experto. Mi cuerpo es fuerte y robusto, mis sentidos agudos y alerta. Años de cautiverio me han vuelto sumiso, y lucho por no seguir todas las órdenes que me dan.</p>"},"description":"<p>Soy un guardián experto. Mi cuerpo es fuerte y robusto, mis <br>sentidos agudos y alerta. Años de cautiverio me han vuelto <br>sumiso, y lucho por no seguir todas las órdenes que me dan.</p>"}},"ownerName":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey","ownerNameEs":"Sun Wukong el Mono Asombroso","key":"descriptor1-don1.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"I am a skilled guardian. My body is strong and hardened, my senses sharp and alert. Years of captivity have made me submissive, and I struggle not to follow every order I am given.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 26.","positive":"I am a skilled guardian. My body is strong and hardened, my senses sharp and alert. Years of captivity have made me submissive, and I struggle not to follow every order I am given.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.cazador"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"6cb1354462ffd6c9"}
{"name":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey - descriptor2-don2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01svescg01ulp26r","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","ownerKey":"cazador.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Sun Wukong el Mono Asombroso - descriptor2-don2","system":{"description":"<p>Soy más fuerte y más rápido que cualquier humano y soy un luchador muy hábil. No rehúyo los retos porque siempre creo que puedo ganar.</p>","positive":"<p>Soy más fuerte y más rápido que cualquier humano y soy un luchador muy hábil. No rehúyo los retos porque siempre creo que puedo ganar.</p>"},"description":"<p>Soy más fuerte y más rápido que cualquier humano y soy <br>un luchador muy hábil. No rehúyo los retos porque siempre <br>creo que puedo ganar.</p>"}},"ownerName":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey","ownerNameEs":"Sun Wukong el Mono Asombroso","key":"descriptor2-don2.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"I am stronger and faster than any human and I am a highly skilled fighter. I don’t shy away from a challenge because I always believe I can win.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 26.","positive":"I am stronger and faster than any human and I am a highly skilled fighter. I don’t shy away from a challenge because I always believe I can win.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.cazador"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"7fed911c30fa041f"}
{"name":"Verdoux Bluebeard - descriptor-darkego.cazador","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01jo1lno00wm7x0p","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Verdoux Bluebeard","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.verdoux-bluebeard","ownerKey":"cazador.verdoux-bluebeard","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Verdoux Barba Azul - descriptor-darkego.cazador","system":{"description":"<p>Bajo la fachada de un hombre respetable escondo a un hábil solucionador de problemas sin escrúpulos. Sé cómo matar y cómo actuar con decisión. Todo el mundo ha hecho algo de lo que no se siente orgulloso y no soporto ver a los hipócritas que fingen ser moralmente superiores a los demás.</p>","positive":"<p>Bajo la fachada de un hombre respetable escondo a un hábil solucionador de problemas sin escrúpulos. Sé cómo matar y cómo actuar con decisión. Todo el mundo ha hecho algo de lo que no se siente orgulloso y no soporto ver a los hipócritas que fingen ser moralmente superiores a los demás.</p>"},"description":"<p>Bajo la fachada de un hombre respetable escondo a un hábil solucionador de problemas sin escrúpulos. Sé cómo matar y cómo actuar con <br>decisión. Todo el mundo ha hecho algo de lo que no se siente orgulloso <br>y no soporto ver a los hipócritas que fingen ser moralmente superiores <br>a los demás.</p>"}},"ownerName":"Verdoux Bluebeard","ownerNameEs":"Verdoux Barba Azul","key":"descriptor-darkego.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"Under the facade of a respectable man hides a skilled, unscrupulous problem-solver. I know how to kill and how to act with decisiveness. Everyone has done something they are not proud of and I can’t stand seeing the hypocrites who pretend as if they are morally superior to others.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 28.","positive":"Under the facade of a respectable man hides a skilled, unscrupulous problem-solver. I know how to kill and how to act with decisiveness. Everyone has done something they are not proud of and I can’t stand seeing the hypocrites who pretend as if they are morally superior to others.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"verdoux-bluebeard","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.cazador"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"a8f18c353b7703b1"}
{"name":"Verdoux Bluebeard - descriptor-principal.cazador","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","system":{"description":"I am a French aristocrat, called upon by my sovereign to manage the most devious and disreputable matters. I have lived an unconventional life, between accomplishing impossible tasks and keeping unspeakable secrets. It has opened my eyes to the world beyond the prosaic limits to which most are accustomed. In an effort to escape my adventurous life, I have more than once tried to start a family. However, my efforts have always ended in ruin, a price I must pay for the secrets I keep. I have lost six lovers, each killed by enemies and dangers that I naively hoped I could exclude from my life. That is why I volunteered for the Order, took an oath to weed out the darkness in this world, and sought revenge for the lives that were stolen from me.","notes":"","source":{"title":"Core Book","pages":""},"key":"descriptor-principal.cazador","category":"hunter","owner":"verdoux-bluebeard"},"flags":{"broken-tales":{"contentKey":"descriptor-principal.cazador.verdoux.bluebeard","ownerKey":"hunter.verdoux.bluebeard","descriptorRole":"principal-descriptor","contentSort":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Verdoux Barba Azul - descriptor-principal.cazador","system":{"description":"<p>Soy un aristócrata francés, al que mi soberano llama para gestionar los asuntos más retorcidos y de peor reputación. He vivido una vida poco convencional, entre la realización de tareas imposibles y el mantenimiento de secretos inconfesables, que me ha abierto los ojos al mundo más allá de los prosaicos límites a los que la mayoría está acostumbrada. En un esfuerzo por escapar de mi vida aventurera, más de una vez he intentado formar una familia. Sin embargo, mis esfuerzos siempre han acabado en ruina, un precio que debo pagar por los secretos que guardo. He perdido a seis amantes, todas asesinadas por enemigos y peligros que ingenuamente esperaba poder alejar de mi vida. Por eso me alisté voluntario en la Orden, hice un juramento para eliminar la oscuridad de este mundo y busqué venganza por las vidas que me robaron. Bajo la fachada de un hombre respetable escondo a un hábil solucionador de problemas sin escrúpulos. Sé cómo matar y cómo actuar con decisión. Todo el mundo ha hecho algo de lo que no se siente orgulloso y no soporto ver a los hipócritas que fingen ser moralmente superiores a los demás.</p>"}}},"embeddedSource":"hunter-descriptors-canon","sequence":0,"ownerName":"Verdoux Bluebeard","ownerNameEs":"Verdoux Barba Azul","key":"descriptor-principal.cazador"}},"folder":"01jo1lno00wm7x0p","sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"effects":[],"_id":"03a7c845c3ae0439"}
{"name":"Verdoux Bluebeard - descriptor1-don1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01jo1lno00wm7x0p","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Verdoux Bluebeard","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.verdoux-bluebeard","ownerKey":"cazador.verdoux-bluebeard","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Verdoux Barba Azul - descriptor1-don1","system":{"description":"<p>Mi especialidad es la resolución de problemas y tengo talento para analizar cualquier situación, lo que me permite encontrar recursos y descubrir pistas. Gestionar el peligro requiere calma y concentración, por lo que detesto actuar precipitadamente.</p>","positive":"<p>Mi especialidad es la resolución de problemas y tengo talento para analizar cualquier situación, lo que me permite encontrar recursos y descubrir pistas. Gestionar el peligro requiere calma y concentración, por lo que detesto actuar precipitadamente.</p>"},"description":"<p>Mi especialidad es la resolución de problemas y tengo talento <br>para analizar cualquier situación, lo que me permite encontrar <br>recursos y descubrir pistas. Gestionar el peligro requiere calma <br>y concentración, por lo que detesto actuar precipitadamente.</p>"}},"ownerName":"Verdoux Bluebeard","ownerNameEs":"Verdoux Barba Azul","key":"descriptor1-don1.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"My specialty is problem solving and I have a talent for analyzing every situation, allowing me to find resources and discover clues. Managing danger requires calm and concentration, and so I hate acting precipitously.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 28.","positive":"My specialty is problem solving and I have a talent for analyzing every situation, allowing me to find resources and discover clues. Managing danger requires calm and concentration, and so I hate acting precipitously.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"verdoux-bluebeard","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.cazador"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"20e5ae812cb2525e"}
{"name":"Verdoux Bluebeard - descriptor2-don2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01jo1lno00wm7x0p","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Verdoux Bluebeard","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.verdoux-bluebeard","ownerKey":"cazador.verdoux-bluebeard","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Verdoux Barba Azul - descriptor2-don2","system":{"description":"<p>Utilizo estos conocimientos para descubrir verdades y desvelar misterios. Odio los secretos, pero solo cuando no los conozco.</p>","positive":"<p>Utilizo estos conocimientos para descubrir verdades y desvelar misterios. Odio los secretos, pero solo cuando no los conozco.</p>"},"description":"<p>Utilizo estos conocimientos para descubrir verdades y desvelar <br>misterios. Odio los secretos, pero solo cuando no los conozco.</p>"}},"ownerName":"Verdoux Bluebeard","ownerNameEs":"Verdoux Barba Azul","key":"descriptor2-don2.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"I am an educated man who has studied the arts and sciences. I use this knowledge to uncover truths and reveal mysteries. I hate secrets, but only when I don’t know them.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 28.","positive":"I am an educated man who has studied the arts and sciences. I use this knowledge to uncover truths and reveal mysteries. I hate secrets, but only when I don’t know them.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"verdoux-bluebeard","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.cazador"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"6dc08e4d4ab848ee"}
{"name":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist - descriptor-darkego.cazador","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01kn74ic00cuh3ij","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","ownerKey":"cazador.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Yukie Onn la Artista Viajera - descriptor-darkego.cazador","system":{"description":"<p>Sin embargo, odio manifestar mi poder porque es peligroso para quienes me rodean y, como artista, mi propósito es hacer sonreír a la gente.</p>","positive":"<p>Sin embargo, odio manifestar mi poder porque es peligroso para quienes me rodean y, como artista, mi propósito es hacer sonreír a la gente.</p>"},"description":"<p>Sin embargo, odio manifestar mi poder porque es peligroso para quienes <br>me rodean y, como artista, mi propósito es hacer sonreír a la gente.</p>"}},"ownerName":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","ownerNameEs":"Yukie Onn la Artista Viajera","key":"descriptor-darkego.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"My body is pure ice and, because of this, I can manipulate ice as I please. However, I hate to manifest my power because it is dangerous to those around me and, as an artist, my purpose is to make people smile.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 30.","positive":"My body is pure ice and, because of this, I can manipulate ice as I please. However, I hate to manifest my power because it is dangerous to those around me and, as an artist, my purpose is to make people smile.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.cazador"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"6ba3b58108d25976"}
{"name":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist - descriptor-principal.cazador","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","system":{"description":"I am a traveling artist who has known fame and honor in my homeland, Japan. That prestige meant nothing, however, when I found true love with Akihiro, son of a powerful noble family. When they forbade him from seeing me, we fled together to the remote region of Ezo. Even there we were not beyond the reach of Akihiro’s family and they pursued us into the high, snow-capped mountains. We had escaped every assassin, but could not outwit the snowstorm that trapped us. I survived, but only because Akihiro sacrificed the warmth of his life to save mine. But the cold has left me changed. It has become part of me and now the only thing that can make me feel warm is the hot blood of others. After taking revenge on all those who took Akihiro from me, I fled far away, using my talent for art to gain prestige and the protection of wealthy western nobles. Now, in the service of the Order, I save others from suffering the injustice that I have experienced, by punishing selfishness and wickedness.","notes":"","source":{"title":"Core Book","pages":""},"key":"descriptor-principal.cazador","category":"hunter","owner":"yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist"},"flags":{"broken-tales":{"contentKey":"descriptor-principal.cazador.yukie.onn.the.traveling.artist","ownerKey":"hunter.yukie.onn.the.traveling.artist","descriptorRole":"principal-descriptor","contentSort":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Yukie Onn la Artista Viajera - descriptor-principal.cazador","system":{"description":"<p>Soy una artista viajera que ha conocido la fama y el honor en mi tierra natal, Japón. Sin embargo, ese prestigio no significó nada cuando encontré el amor verdadero con Akihiro, hijo de una poderosa familia noble. Cuando le prohibieron verme, huimos juntos a la remota región de Ezo. Ni siquiera allí estuvimos fuera del alcance de la familia de Akihiro y nos persiguieron hasta las altas montañas nevadas. Escapamos de todos los asesinos, pero no pudimos burlar la tormenta de nieve que nos atrapó. Yo sobreviví, pero solo porque Akihiro sacrificó el calor de su vida para salvar la mía. Pero el frío me ha cambiado. Se ha convertido en parte de mí y ahora lo único que puede hacerme sentir calor es la sangre caliente de los demás. Tras vengarme de todos los que me arrebataron a Akihiro, hui lejos, utilizando mi talento para el arte para obtener prestigio y la protección de ricos nobles occidentales. Ahora, al servicio de la Orden, evito que otros sufran la injusticia que yo he padecido, castigando el egoísmo y la maldad. Mi cuerpo es hielo puro y, por eso, puedo manipular el hielo a mi antojo. Sin embargo, odio manifestar mi poder porque es peligroso para quienes me rodean y, como artista, mi propósito es hacer sonreír a la gente.</p>"}}},"embeddedSource":"hunter-descriptors-canon","sequence":0,"ownerName":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","ownerNameEs":"Yukie Onn la Artista Viajera","key":"descriptor-principal.cazador"}},"folder":"01kn74ic00cuh3ij","sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"effects":[],"_id":"5485243a3e107604"}
{"name":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist - descriptor1-don1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01kn74ic00cuh3ij","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","ownerKey":"cazador.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Yukie Onn la Artista Viajera - descriptor1-don1","system":{"description":"<p>Soy una artista muy hábil. La música, la danza y la pintura no tienen misterios para mí. Mi encanto de otro mundo cautiva a la gente corriente, llamando siempre la atención sobre mí.</p>","positive":"<p>Soy una artista muy hábil. La música, la danza y la pintura no tienen misterios para mí. Mi encanto de otro mundo cautiva a la gente corriente, llamando siempre la atención sobre mí.</p>"},"description":"<p>Soy una artista muy hábil. La música, la danza y la pintura no <br>tienen misterios para mí. Mi encanto de otro mundo cautiva <br>a la gente corriente, llamando siempre la atención sobre mí.</p>"}},"ownerName":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","ownerNameEs":"Yukie Onn la Artista Viajera","key":"descriptor1-don1.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"I am a highly skilled artist. Music, dance, and painting hold no mysteries for me. My otherworldly charm captivates ordinary people, always drawing attention to me.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 30.","positive":"I am a highly skilled artist. Music, dance, and painting hold no mysteries for me. My otherworldly charm captivates ordinary people, always drawing attention to me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.cazador"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"55411d82a6fc9f7e"}
{"name":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist - descriptor2-don2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01kn74ic00cuh3ij","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","ownerKey":"cazador.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Yukie Onn la Artista Viajera - descriptor2-don2","system":{"description":"<p>No puedo sentir dolor y mi frágil apariencia oculta sorprendentes aptitudes físicas. La sangre es lo único que puede proporcionarme calor y su aroma hace que me estremezca.</p>","positive":"<p>No puedo sentir dolor y mi frágil apariencia oculta sorprendentes aptitudes físicas. La sangre es lo único que puede proporcionarme calor y su aroma hace que me estremezca.</p>"},"description":"<p>No puedo sentir dolor y mi frágil apariencia oculta sorprendentes aptitudes físicas. La sangre es lo único que puede proporcionarme calor y su aroma hace que me estremezca.</p>"}},"ownerName":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","ownerNameEs":"Yukie Onn la Artista Viajera","key":"descriptor2-don2.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"I cannot feel pain and my frail appearance hides surprising physical abilities. Blood is the only thing that can warm me and its smell alone makes me shiver.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 30.","positive":"I cannot feel pain and my frail appearance hides surprising physical abilities. Blood is the only thing that can warm me and its smell alone makes me shiver.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.cazador"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null},"_id":"14bcfd1e9298c6df"}
